CALENDAR

   Jan. 15: The RTC's deadline for creation of a priority schedule for
thrift resolutions. The agency must also present a working capital proposal
to the House Ways and Means Committee on this date.
   Jan. 18-19: "The RTC Thrift Asset Disposition Conference" is conducted
by Banking Law Institute in Washington. Scheduled speakers include Lamar C.
Kelly Jr., director of RTC's asset and real estate management division.
(800) 831-8333.
   Jan. 23: RTC officials testify before the House Banking Committee. The
Senate Banking Committee conducts hearings Jan. 29.
   Feb. 13-14: "How to Acquire and Manage Real Property Through the RTC" is
the subject of a New York conference sponsored by the Institute for
International Research. (800) 345-8016.
   Feb. 15-16: Banking Law Institute offers a Dallas seminar on RTC asset
disposition and contracting opportunities. (800) 831-8333.
   Mar. 5-7: Pension World and National Real Estate Investor present a
conference on pension funds and real estate, in Scottsdale, Ariz. (404)
256-9800.
   March 30: The Oversight Board's deadline for establishing asset-
disposition policies and procedures.
   Jan. 15: The RTC's deadline for creation of a priority schedule for
thrift resolutions. The agency must also present a working capital proposal
to the House Ways and Means Committee on this date.
   Jan. 18-19: "The RTC Thrift Asset Disposition Conference" is conducted
by Banking Law Institute in Washington. Scheduled speakers include Lamar C.
Kelly Jr., director of RTC's asset and real estate management division.
(800) 831-8333.
   Jan. 23: RTC officials testify before the House Banking Committee. The
Senate Banking Committee conducts hearings Jan. 29.
   Feb. 13-14: "How to Acquire and Manage Real Property Through the RTC" is
the subject of a New York conference sponsored by the Institute for
International Research. (800) 345-8016.
   Feb. 15-16: Banking Law Institute offers a Dallas seminar on RTC asset
disposition and contracting opportunities. (800) 831-8333.
   Mar. 5-7: Pension World and National Real Estate Investor present a
conference on pension funds and real estate, in Scottsdale, Ariz. (404)
256-9800.
   March 30: The Oversight Board's deadline for establishing asset-
disposition policies and procedures.



