THRIFT LIQUIDATION ALERT via NewsNet
January 8, 1990

RTC's Regional Office Network Takes Shape

   It will take a few more months for RTC to finish staffing its regional
offices, though most key management positions have already been filled at
the four locations.
   Next on the agenda is building a network of consolidated field offices,
where much of the contracting work is expected to take place. The east and
central regions have begun organizing field offices, while the southwest
and west regions have not yet announced sites or managers for their
outposts.

